nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First off he probably should duck the first 2 diamonds. Even if he takes the first diamond, he should lead a spade and continue spades. If speads break 3-3 he will take 4 spades, 1 diamond, 3 hearts, and 1 club for 9 tricks. |
