nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If spades are not 3-3, then he has 2 spades, 1 diamond, 3 hearts, and a club for sure. That's 7 so he needs 2 more tricks. So if spades are not 3-3 he has to hope the club finesse works. |
