nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Note that he would give himself an extra chance by ducking 2 diamonds because if North has both the @SA and @CK, he has no diamonds to lead back and, therefore, the contract will still make. So planning was a bit complicated though doable.|
